# Image placeholder folder

Replace these with actual screenshots / banner / GIFs.

Recommended files:
- banner.png         (1280×640 hero image, used in README)
- scanner-running.png   (Flipper screen — scanner active)
- scanner-maxhold.png   (Flipper screen — MAX HOLD state)
- scanner-paused.png    (Flipper screen — PAUSE state)
- error-screen.png      (Flipper screen — Board Not Detected)
- ui-anatomy.png        (UI annotated with zone labels)
- demo.gif              (10s animation: scanning + cursor + max hold)
- product-shot.png      (Flipper + PINGEQUA board, photography)

When ready:
1. Place files in this folder
2. Verify README and docs/ references resolve
3. Delete this .gitkeep
